name: Tegridy Stan
description:
South Park Boys: Limited edition

"You know, I learned something today." is what Stan always said. The dude just needs to input his analog to make us "Feel" something. But in reality, Stan is a very caring and sensitive boy. He goes vegan after he found out cows were torture and stuff. At least he is making a difference by always remind his friend to do better. So in a way, Stan is cool! If you got a friend like Stan, you just found a long lifetime friend! Plus, his dad sells weed!
